{"tid":1270563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"升旗儀式宣佈「因天雨關係」改室內通過電視屏幕觀看升旗儀式   林鄭穿黑衣致詞笑容牽強","createTime":"2019-07-01T01:03:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T02:56:13.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d8f83d7b09bdbe10fa4ae45c58d44459e0b4eec6","tid":1270563,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T01:03:15.000Z","msg":"升旗儀式因天雨改室內進行 林鄭穿黑衣致詞笑容牽強<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190701/large/1561941995_5d01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190701%2Flarge%2F1561941995_5d01.png&h=07730ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭身穿黑衣致詞，她指近日修例爭議，令她徹底明白作為從政者，需警醒自己要準確掌握民情。Now TV新聞台影片截圖<br />\n<br />\n網民發起「不舉行動」，號召市民於7.1早上6時半到灣仔金紫荊「用多國語言與國歌和音，萬人合唱。」港島主幹道龍和道、夏慤道凌晨時份被堵塞。警方在其後接近清晨開始清理障礙。示威者早上未有撤退迹象，今早原訂在金紫荊廣場舉行的升旗儀式，但政府早上6時45分出稿，宣佈「因天雨關係」，升旗儀式改以雨天方案，在室內進行，而嘉賓會安排至在會展3樓大會堂通過電視屏幕觀看升旗儀式，而慶祝酒會則如期舉行。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190701/59775500\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190701%2F59775500&d=YBElpbzmALMQinc%2Bu7edP60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=78ebd81f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190701%2F59775500&h=9184a65d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190701/59775500</a>"},{"pid":"46aa14a52cb531f8b5b54b5607ebc0edb45f7659","tid":1270563,"uid":93060,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T01:04:33.000Z","msg":"表面係白 內裹係黑 港獨之母用心良苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />we connect"},{"pid":"c3fb6f5d31e4abbb8c9a05a172368e9fb0f93588","tid":1270563,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T01:05:00.000Z","msg":"2016國慶落雨擔遮照係金紫荊廣場升旗"},{"pid":"c3e5740e8c590712ed2b58e1d26bd4cfd6bf57c4","tid":1270563,"ui